516
00:43:12,470 --> 00:43:15,370
- And there are still trains running.
- It's too bad.

517
00:43:15,370 --> 00:43:16,900
But have a safe trip home.

518
00:43:16,900 --> 00:43:20,550
- Good night, then.
- Good night.

519
00:43:20,550 --> 00:43:22,480
Good night.

520
00:43:25,810 --> 00:43:28,350
We should both be heading
home, too.

521
00:43:28,350 --> 00:43:32,350
- I'm still okay.
- But...

522
00:43:32,350 --> 00:43:36,160
There's no problem.
We're both adults.

523
00:43:39,630 --> 00:43:43,730
I'm sorry. Maybe I've had too
much to drink.

524
00:43:44,830 --> 00:43:46,170
You!

525
00:43:46,870 --> 00:43:48,690
I'm sorry.

526
00:43:48,690 --> 00:43:52,490
I'm not your type anyway.

527
00:43:54,040 --> 00:43:56,000
My type?

528
00:43:56,640 --> 00:44:00,580
Unfortunately, there seem to be
no women that are my type.

529
00:44:02,150 --> 00:44:04,380
Fujimura<i>-sensei...</i>

530
00:44:05,390 --> 00:44:07,080
Taxi!

531
00:44:11,800 --> 00:44:13,300
Wait!

532
00:44:13,300 --> 00:44:15,030
Was Yûji really laughing?

533
00:44:19,570 --> 00:44:23,170
<i>I was so incredibly lonely.</i>

534
00:44:24,170 --> 00:44:29,810
<i>Everything I did was in vain.
