548
00:47:02,160 --> 00:47:04,190
You recognized me?

549
00:47:05,670 --> 00:47:07,090
Yeah.

550
00:47:08,700 --> 00:47:10,470
Then why?

551
00:47:11,310 --> 00:47:15,010
You're a student, so I figured
