553
00:47:19,380 --> 00:47:21,320
She kissed me.

554
00:47:21,320 --> 00:47:25,020
If a pizza comes that you didn't
order, would you eat it?

555
00:47:25,890 --> 00:47:28,620
- I see what you mean.
- Good!

556
00:47:29,320 --> 00:47:31,830
I didn't think I'd ever
see you again,

557
00:47:31,830 --> 00:47:35,150
so I let some of my weaknesses
show.

558
00:47:35,960 --> 00:47:37,100
Weakness?

559
00:47:38,270 --> 00:47:42,580
That I wanted you to stay
beside me all night.

560
00:47:42,580 --> 00:47:45,570
Like a child who had
a bad dream?

561
00:47:46,110 --> 00:47:49,030
Even though I'm an adult.

562
00:47:49,510 --> 00:47:51,950
So you pretended you didn't
recognize me.

563
00:47:51,950 --> 00:47:53,550
Right.

564
00:47:54,280 --> 00:48:01,520
Not because I'm just some
simple, boring girl?

565
00:48:01,520 --> 00:48:05,020
Huh? No.

566
00:48:07,060 --> 00:48:09,060
That's good.

567
00:48:14,300 --> 00:48:16,140
I...

568
00:48:23,740 --> 00:48:30,890
I'll probably have a normal life,
get married, and have two kids.

569
00:48:30,890 --> 00:48:36,050
Maybe that's supposed to be
happiness, but what if it isn't?

570
00:48:37,420 --> 00:48:42,060
For some reason I just started
thinking that way.

571
00:48:42,560 --> 00:48:45,660
I wanted a secret all
for myself.

572
00:48:47,300 --> 00:48:49,070
A secret?

573
00:48:50,100 --> 00:48:52,800
Even if I'm not happy
in that new life,

574
00:48:52,800 --> 00:48:56,100
I would have a secret
from my past.

575
00:48:57,750 --> 00:49:00,280
But why do you want that?

576
00:49:01,550 --> 00:49:07,650
My father was laid off, and my
whole family was left suffering.

577
00:49:09,720 --> 00:49:11,420
I just don't know.

578
00:49:12,660 --> 00:49:17,290
I would like to go back to being
my normal self.

579
00:49:18,130 --> 00:49:22,990
If only I had that secret
to take with me.

580
00:49:24,070 --> 00:49:29,060
But if the only person that shares
that secret with me...

581
00:49:29,060 --> 00:49:33,210
...doesn't remember it,
there's no point.

582
00:49:39,890 --> 00:49:43,950
I'm happy that you
remembered.

